title: EaseUS Partition Mastenician 11.5 WinPE Edition (x64)
description:
EaseUS Partition Master Technician 11.5 WinPE Edition (x64)

Disk Management Solution for IT Service Provider which costs less than competitors with more robust features. It allows to provide technical service to clients with unlimited usage for disk management, partition recovery and clone.	

Key Features:
Best solution to create, delete, resize/move, merge, split, wipe or format partitions to make better use of hard drive capacity.

â€¢	Convert primary partition to logical partition and vice versa: convert a primary volume to logical to create a fifth volume on a disk with 4 existed primary volumes.
â€¢	Linux partition management: Easily delete, create, format, recover EXT2/EXT3 partition, etc.
â€¢	Create WinPE rescue disk for booting sickly computer.
â€¢	Speed up your computer by defragmentation.

Disk & Partition Copy Wizard
Easily copy disk partition, dynamic volume or GPT partition for data protection or disk upgrade, no Windows system reinstallation required.

â€¢	Migrate OS to SSD without reinstalling Windows
â€¢	Copy partition with fast file-by-file copy to protect your data
â€¢	Clone entire hard disk to another without Windows reinstallation
â€¢	Upgrade system disk to a bigger one with one-click.

Partition Recovery Wizard
Partition Recovery Wizard built-in EaseUS Partition Master is designed to recover deleted or lost partitions.

â€¢	Recover deleted or lost partitions from unallocated space due to any personal, hardware or software failure or virus attack.

â€¢	Two recovery modes in Partition Recovery Wizard: Automatic recovery mode and Manual recovery mode.
â€¢	Supports FAT, NTFS, EXT2 & EXT3 partition recovery.
